{
  "texts": [
    "Xuanwumen Street, adjacent to Xuanwu Lake and Jiming Temple, is another important landmark area.",
    "Meiyuan New Village Street is an essential historical and cultural district with profound cultural heritage.",
    "In Yuhuatai District, the China (Nanjing) Software Valley, a national software industry base, is home to numerous high-tech enterprises, reflecting the city's collective memory in industrial transformation and technological innovation in the new era.",
    "Outside the main urban areas, some suburban regions in Nanjing also exhibit certain collective memory characteristics.",
    "In Pukou District, the area under the management of the Pearl Spring Committee is home to Pearl Spring Scenic Area and Pukou Laoshan Forest Park, reflecting a memory feature dominated by natural landscapes."
  ]
}